title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 9 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jul 9 2021
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 3: Clay Travis: Is it fair to compare Afghanistan to Vietnam? More thoughts from Afghanistan combat veterans. Rush's Timeless Wisdom on the Orwellian NSA surveillance of the American people. Tucker Carlson calls in to talk about the NSA surveillance and their possible plan to discredit him. This isn't about Tucker, if the spying happened to Rachel Maddow, Tucker would still be calling for an investigation. The Russian withdrawal from Afghanistan was much different from the US.
